⚙️ AI Fitness Coach Automation (Step-by-Step)
🧠 Workflow Overview

Trigger → Collect Input → AI Processing → Output → Follow-up

🔹 STEP 1: Trigger (Start Automation)

Choose how users interact:

Webhook (best for apps)
Telegram bot
WhatsApp (via API)
Form (Google Forms)

👉 Example:

User sends: weight loss, 70kg, 170cm, beginner
🔹 STEP 2: Input Parser

Split user input into fields:

Goal → weight loss / muscle gain
Weight → 70
Height → 170
Experience → beginner

👉 In n8n:

Use Set Node or Function Node
🔹 STEP 3: Validation (Important)

Check:

Weight is number
Height is number
Goal is valid

👉 If invalid:
➡️ Send error message:
"Please send in correct format: goal, weight, height, experience"

🔹 STEP 4: AI Processing (Core Step)

Use OpenAI / LLM node:

Prompt:

You are an AI Fitness Coach.

User:
Goal: {{$json.goal}}
Weight: {{$json.weight}}
Height: {{$json.height}}
Experience: {{$json.experience}}

Give:
1. Weekly workout plan
2. Indian diet plan
3. Daily motivation

Keep it simple.
🔹 STEP 5: Format Output

Structure response:

🏋️ Workout Plan
🥗 Diet Plan
💪 Motivation

👉 Optional:
Use a Function Node to format nicely

🔹 STEP 6: Send Response

Send back via:

Telegram message
WhatsApp reply
Web app response
🔹 STEP 7: Store User Data (Optional but Powerful)

Save in:

Google Sheets
Airtable
Database

Store:

Name
Goal
Plan
Date
🔹 STEP 8: Daily Automation (Smart Feature)

Add Cron Node (daily)

➡️ Send:

Daily workout reminder
Motivation quote
Diet tip
🔹 STEP 9: Progress Tracking (Advanced)

Every week:

Ask weight update
Compare progress
Generate new plan
